1. *Tommy* je bio najbolji učenik u školi. (*Tommy* was the best student in the school.)
2. *Tommy* je završio svoju misiju. (*Tommy* completed his mission.)
3. *Tommy* je rekao da će odmoriti. (*Tommy* said he would take a break.)
4. *Tommy* je imao veliki plan. (*Tommy* had a big plan.)
5. *Tommy*ova kuća bila je velika. (*Tommy's* house was big.)
6. *Tommy*ov prijatelj je bio tužan. (*Tommy's* friend was sad.)
7. *Tommy* će raditi večeras. (*Tommy* will be working tonight.)
8. *Tommy* je dobio odgovor. (*Tommy* got an answer.)